@Type("realnumeric") public sealed interface PsyRealNumeric extends PsyNumeric, PsyConvertableToInteger, PsyConvertableToIntegral, PsyConvertableToRational, PsyConvertableToReal, PsyScalar<PsyRealNumeric> permits PsyRational, PsyReal
The representation of realnumeric, an abstraction of real number.
